## 5. Dynamic Features (Client‑side JavaScript)

The generated page includes a single large inline script (`BusTimetableApp` class) that provides:
- Real‑time clock update.
- Tab switching and persistence.
- Search filtering (cards or bus stops).
- Alphabet navigation (scroll‑to, highlight, active letter detection).
- Time filter buttons.
- Next bus highlighting (runs every 30 seconds, checks all time bubbles on depot pages).
- Advanced search modal (global search over divisions, districts, tehsils, depots) using `search-index.js`.
- Blog link handler for URL constants.
- Scroll‑spy for vertical alphabet.

